skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: worlds awakening radio
des:
Hello and Welcome to Worlds Awakening Radio! 

We at Worlds Awakening are delighted that you have joined us and hope that you enjoy your time listening to our variety of shows and music. Whatever your taste in tunes, we reckon that there will be something on our station that will tickle your fancy. It could be Country, it might be Chutney, It could be Rock, or maybe a bit of Pop!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
